<HEADLINE>
OLIVE OYL, POPEYE TAKE THE PLUNGE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients)  
By MARLA MATZER 
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Comic books have always played out the fantasies
