<HEADLINE>
YUGOSLAV CROWN PRINCE: KOSOVO IS ONLY PART OF BALKANS' PROBLEM  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (TIMELY! Commentary...Resending from Feb. 19)   (This timely 1,150-word ``separate buy'' commentary by Crown Prince
Alexander of Yugoslavia is from the International Herald
Tribune.)  
  
