<HEADLINE>
COURT MAKES IT MORE DIFFICULT TO SUE NCAA 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By MARK HELM  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
