Oakland Congressman Ron Dellums, which focuses on Dellums'
commitment to pacifism. The nephew of C.L. Dellums, a leader of the
mid-century civil rights group Brotherhood of Sleeping Porters,
Dellums said his uncle was an early influence on his advocacy of
nuclear deterrence and opposition to the Vietnam War. Stricherz
