<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-DRAGGING-DEATH-NYT, which moved
in ``a'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``We are very relieved at the moment, but we still have some
healing to do.''
</P>
<P>
   R.C. HORN, mayor of Jasper, Texas, after the conviction of a
white man in the dragging death of a black man.
</P>
