<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-23 22:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6677 &Cx1f; tic-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-AF-RECRUIT-AZR &LR;      02-23 1029
